{"tid":1815772,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"電動鐵騎香港應唔應該買嚟揸？","createTime":"2020-01-07T18:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T11:07:49.000Z","uid":259758,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a76def64d73832e867f59a9e015e2061d6bb317f","tid":1815772,"uid":259758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"利申：未考鐵騎牌，考完牌先買。<br />\n個人迷鐵騎，更極迷電動車，但電動鐵騎都係第一次聽聞。<br />\n啱啱睄到Zero有新2020 Model，叫SR/F，個人認為極度吸引。Google咗先知原來09年已經有電動鐵騎，14年Model比康文署佢哋用ZF9（9 kW），16年有ZF13.0（13 kW），新嘅SR/F就ZF14.4（14 kW）。<br />\n想問下各位師兄香港好唔好揸電動鐵騎？引擎無聲好似無咩存在感，但係慳油錢我覺得唔錯（雖然慳唔得幾多）。"},{"pid":"3589e5d61d2d0387627048b97f66b4b50f802348","tid":1815772,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:40:24.000Z","msg":"買hoverboard <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ecb674d41281389231f87e2808769cc0a85d09","tid":1815772,"uid":259758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3589e5d61d2d0387627048b97f66b4b50f802348","tid":1815772,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:40:24.000Z","msg":"買hoverboard <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:08:41.000Z","msg":"都幾離地喎（錢）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee28c49a1745d225468aec56460f6d7c8b8b8f5","tid":1815772,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"1.你要屋企自己有叉電位<br />\n2.Zero好多recall"},{"pid":"ee962c360ff417cdc879f3b2811ff29e4b466697","tid":1815772,"uid":114064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T03:48:58.000Z","msg":"電動輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59766e849782dce88bfc984d94523309ae33919e","tid":1815772,"uid":259877,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"電單車既聲 隨時救你一命"},{"pid":"8cfead5c327700f22dae1ac7ec9c934f2